                    LIFEMAXXING — FINAL IMPLEMENTATION PLAN
================================================================================
Status: locked to current outline (see cross-references below). Update this file
when outline taxonomy or v1 scope intentionally changes.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. PRODUCT
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
macOS SwiftUI app that tracks life progress: skill-category habits/tasks (EXP,
mastery, stardust), three main questlines (long-term goals), weekly quest
bundles, shop/wishlists, and a map-style deadline view. Design intent lives in:
  - dashboardOutline          → primary dashboard layout & Mental Health entry
  - Main Properties            → EXP, mastery, stardust, skill tasks, Map, Shop
  - MainQuestlines/format      → questline page structure & entities
  - Shop, Map                  → economy & calendar behaviors
  - WeeklyQuests/format        → repeating weekly bundle schema

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2. CANONICAL TAXONOMY (no ValueMaxxing; three questlines only)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Skill categories (v1 domains):
  • Mental Health      — SkillCategories/MentalHealth/*, Journal, mood, wins
  • Personal Care      — SkillCategories/PersonalCare/*
  • Household & Chores — SkillCategories/HouseholdAndChores/*, Shopping List

Per-category pattern (Main Properties):
  main hub, wishlist (feeds Shop), timescale/deadlines, skill tasks.

Main questlines (exactly three):
  • Academia (BrainMaxxing folder / hub) — MainQuestlines/BrainMaxxing/main
  • FinMaxxing  — MainQuestlines/FinMaxxing/main
  • FitMaxxing  — MainQuestlines/FitMaxxing/main

Weekly quests: definitions under WeeklyQuests/ (e.g. everythingShower,
biweeklyBudget); shared properties in WeeklyQuests/format.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3. DATA ENTITIES (implementation targets)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Skill layer:
  SkillCategory, SkillTask (deadline-capable), optional EXP/stardust awards,
  MasteryLevel / EXP thresholds per category.

Mental Health:
  MoodLogEntry; JournalEntry (Name, Created Date, category enum: thoughts &
  introspection, planning, rants and raves, big sad, daily entry); DailyEntry
  fields: brain dump, affirmation, task dump, notes; WinEntry (wins list).

Household:
  Shopping list rows (Item, Status: !P1/!P2/!P3/Pending/Purchased); views:
  meta, groceries, wishlist, archive; append-only knowledge: ingredient list,
  meals & recipes (recipe ↔ ingredients checkmarks).

Questlines:
  Questline, Objective, Quest (deadline), Subquest (deadline), ToDo database
  links as in format file.

Economy:
  WishlistItem / Shop product fields per Shop + Properties/wishlist; stardust
  pools per skill category; unlock rules when stardust meter fills.

Map:
  Aggregated items with deadlines: skill tasks, quests, subtasks (optional
  external calendar sync is post–v1 unless you pull it forward).

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
